We claim that our analysis is valid for different types of oscillations, no just magnitude constantly moving walls. Indeed, we can numerically solve the Schrödinger equation for a particle in a periodically varying box, but with a more continuously varying oscillation. To do so, we use a similar algorithm to the one proposed by Doescher et al.12 Let us introduce the ansatz
